.com%2Fb7%2Fab%2F12765e904c2ea3d54163e60ed31e%2F2025-01-16-npr-mps-098-final.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1687+0+313/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb7%2Fab%2F12765e904c2ea3d54163e60ed31e%2F2025-01-16-npr-mps-098-final.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1687+0+313/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb7%2Fab%2F12765e904c2ea3d54163e60ed31e%2F2025-01-16-npr-mps-098-final.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1687+0+313/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb7%2Fab%2F12765e904c2ea3d54163e60ed31e%2F2025-01-16-npr-mps-098-final.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1687+0+313/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb7%2Fab%2F12765e904c2ea3d54163e60ed31e%2F2025-01-16-npr-mps-098-final.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1687+0+313/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb7%2Fab%2F12765e904c2ea3d54163e60ed31e%2F2025-01-16-npr-mps-098-final.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1687+0+313/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb7%2Fab%2F12765e904c2ea3d54163e60ed31e%2F2025-01-16-npr-mps-098-final.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1687+0+313/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb7%2Fab%2F12765e904c2ea3d54163e60ed31e%2F2025-01-16-npr-mps-098-final.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;           