s1-5262993/snl-makeup-designer-louie-zakarian" target="_blank"&gt;learn about the method behind the madness&lt;/a&gt; that created Kyle Mooney's Baby Yoda, Will Ferrell's devil and more.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-48473" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 2958;         --source-height: 1664;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2958x1664+0+660/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb9%2F0a%2F78159dce4cd6849635a55d8dc0dd%2Finfrared-image-of-portrait-of-mateu-fernandez-de-soto-department-of-conservation-the-courtauld-institute-of-art-london.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2958x1664+0+660/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb9%2F0a%2F78159dce4cd6849635a55d8dc0dd%2Finfrared-image-of-portrait-of-mateu-fernandez-de-soto-department-of-conservation-the-courtauld-institute-of-art-london.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2958x1664+0+660/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb9%2F0a%2F78159dce4cd6849635a55d8dc0dd%2Finfrared-image-of-portrait-of-mateu-fernandez-de-soto-department-of-conservation-the-courtauld-institute-of-art-london.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2958x1664+0+660/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb9%2F0a%2F78159dce4cd6849635a55d8dc0dd%2Finfrared-image-of-portrait-of-mateu-fernandez-de-soto-department-of-conservation-the-courtauld-institute-of-art-london.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2958x1664+0+660/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?u