er-in-matthew-rushings-sacred-songs-photo-by-danica-paulos-96.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3801x2138+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2Ffc%2Fbc70bef54e22977c2dbbf3a85af1%2Falvin-ailey-american-dance-theater-in-matthew-rushings-sacred-songs-photo-by-danica-paulos-96.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3801x2138+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2Ffc%2Fbc70bef54e22977c2dbbf3a85af1%2Falvin-ailey-american-dance-theater-in-matthew-rushings-sacred-songs-photo-by-danica-paulos-96.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3801x2138+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2Ffc%2Fbc70bef54e22977c2dbbf3a85af1%2Falvin-ailey-american-dance-theater-in-matthew-rushings-sacred-songs-photo-by-danica-paulos-96.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3801x2138+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2Ffc%2Fbc70bef54e22977c2dbbf3a85af1%2Falvin-ailey-american-dance-theater-in-matthew-rushings-sacred-songs-photo-by-danica-paulos-96.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3801x2138+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2Ffc%2Fbc70bef54e22977c2dbbf3a85af1%2Falvin-ailey-american-dance-theater-in-matthew-rushings-sacred-songs-photo-by-danica-paulos-96.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3801x2138+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2Ffc%2Fbc70bef54e22977c2dbbf3a85af1%2Falvin-ailey-american-dance-theater-in-matthew-rushings-sacred-songs-photo-by-danica-paulos-96.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3801x2138+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2Ffc%2Fbc70bef54e22977c2dbbf3a85af1%2Falvin-ailey-american-dance-theater-in-matthew-rushings-sacred-songs-photo-by-danica-paulos-96.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3801x2138+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2Ffc%2Fbc70bef54e22977c2dbbf3a85af1%2Falvin-ailey-american-dance-theater-in-matthew-rushings-sacred-songs-photo-by-danica-paulos-96.jpg" class="img" alt="The Alvin Ailey American Dance Theater performs Sacred Songs, choreographed by interim artistic director Matthew Rushing based on material featured in the original 1960 version of the company&amp;#039;s Revelations." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 The Alvin Ailey American Dance Theater performs &lt;em&gt;Sacred Songs&lt;/em&gt;, choreographed by interim artistic director Matthew Rushing based on material featured in the original 1960 version of the company's &lt;em&gt;Revelations&lt;/em&gt;.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Danica Paulos Photography                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Modern dance choreographer Alvin Ailey was only 29 when he created &lt;em&gt;Revelations&lt;/em&gt; based on his childhood memories. Set to traditional Black spirituals, work songs and blues tunes, the dance performance reflects the Black experience through its story of faith and perseverance from the trials of slavery to freedom. When it was first performed in 1960, it was about twice as long as the version that's now been seen by millions of people worldwide. The Alvin Ailey American Dance Theater is revisiting the work with a new piece set to fresh interpretations of the songs that were removed. &lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;🎧 Listen to snippets from the show and learn about how the newly resurrected songs aim to &lt;a href="http://one.npr.org/?sharedMediaId=nx-s1-5279458:x" target="_blank"&gt;resonate with a contemporary, young audience&lt;/a&gt;. Read more about the show and see photos of the production &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/12/nx-s1-5279458/lost-songs-from-alvin-aileys-revelations-find-voice-in-new-piece" target="_blank"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;Live advice&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-46875" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 7952;         --source-height: 4473;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/1800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/webp" /&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/400/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/7952x4473+0+352/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff8%2F34%2Ffd4a45f54c88b39036b2435fc728%2Fgettyimages-2150049791.jpg" class="img" alt="A paper craft style illustration of layered red hearts inset in a white speech bubble on a red background. " loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 At Life Kit, we've heard a lot of relationship advice over the years. These seven pieces of advice from sex and relationship therapists stuck with us.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          MirageC/Getty Images/Moment RF                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;If you're celebrating a romantic relationship this week for Valentine's Day, you probably know that while relationships can be magical, they can also be hard work. Whether you just started dating or you're decades into a marriage, consider this advice relationship experts shared with NPR for &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/11/nx-s1-5288794/9-pieces-of-advice-to-help-you-navigate-the-ups-and-downs-of-romance" target="_blank"&gt;keeping the love flowing&lt;/a&gt; through life's ups and downs. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;ul class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;❤️ How do you know if they're "the one?" Look for someone who wants to celebrate the things you find important, says Mandy Len Catron, author of the essay collection &lt;em&gt;How to Fall in Love with Anyone&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;❤️ Keep a ratio of five times as many positive emotions to negative emotions during a conflict, says relationship researcher and clinical psychologist John Gottman. Expressing interest in a discussion and making eye contact lubricate the wheels of communication.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;❤️ Many people think that once they meet their person, they'll be much happier. But that's not how happiness works, according to clinical psychologist Jenny Taitz. Your relationship status has nothing to do with your worth.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Read more expert advice on love, including &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/11/nx-s1-5288794/9-pieces-of-advice-to-help-you-navigate-the-ups-and-downs-of-romance" target="_blank"&gt;how to create intimacy&lt;/a&gt; when you don't have time for sex and how to know when it's time to break up.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;       &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-48320" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 2700;         --source-height: 1519;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2700x1519+0+141/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F64%2F46%2F4d3d19ab40dba0bfe96b88e4b4ca%2Fgettyimages-2258151.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2700x1519+0+141/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F64%2F46%2F4d3d19ab40dba0bfe96b88e4b4ca%2Fgettyimages-2258151.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2700x1519+0+141/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F64%2F46%2F4d3d19ab40dba0bfe96b88e4b4ca%2Fgettyimages-2258151.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2700x1519+0+141/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F64%2F46%2F4d3d19ab40dba0bfe96b88e4b4ca%2Fgettyimages-2258151.jpg 9