in some memorable looks. Check out &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/the-picture-show/2025/02/02/g-s1-46115/photos-see-all-the-red-carpet-looks-from-the-67th-grammy-awards" target="_blank"&gt;photos of these looks&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;ul class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;➡️ Here's the &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/02/nx-s1-5280335/2025-grammy-awards-full-list-nominees-and-winners" target="_blank"&gt;complete list of winners&lt;/a&gt; at the 67th Grammy Awards.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;➡️ Before they were Grammy winners, they were Tiny Desk performers. Watch some of their shows &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/03/g-s1-45827/2025-grammy-awards-tiny-desk-concert" target="_blank"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-45785" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 3500;         --source-height: 1969;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr